{"tid":1441704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憤怒文宣","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T00:47:50.000Z","uid":74259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"413ffeab6c1040d5402c598fba1f8e2ce0deccd8","tid":1441704,"uid":74259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"詳情見上一個POST <br />\n對家打民生牌 我地更加要打民生牌<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436221</a><br />\n<br />\n我地目標應該係唔好俾機會政府回應 日日唔同topic 佢一準備好回應我地就已經去左新 Topic 令政府進退失據 建立政府無能的形象<br />\n <br />\n依一個文宣目的係 打擊政整體形象 所以會冷飯新事一次過上 令更多人不滿政府 將今次運動升級做所有群體的民怨爆發<br />\n<br />\n好似我上一個POST咁講 動之以情，說之以理可以說服到人支持我地 但係激起對政府憤怒可能可以connect到另一班人 由其是個班仲未醒的港豬<br />\n<br />\n小弟唔識創作 淨係用WORD整左兩張草圖 希望大家可以一齊討論依個方向可唔可行 最後係希望可以係唔同區派 接觸更多受眾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww01pVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww01pVW.png&h=35293afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnUJDfW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnUJDfW.png&h=0b159028&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e00c2aadde76a3ca3dc8522c85a122bb3046367d","tid":1441704,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:21:29.000Z","msg":"太多字"},{"pid":"4ab70e1837140e77576d662a04720d0c893895c6","tid":1441704,"uid":74259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"PUSH <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6590a6e4e077470a987850a90b592062264df46","tid":1441704,"uid":74259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e00c2aadde76a3ca3dc8522c85a122bb3046367d","tid":1441704,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:21:29.000Z","msg":"太多字"},"citedBy":0,"rep